data.description: Back on the market! Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this captivating 4 bed 2.5 bath residence in Thornton offers a fantastic blend of comfort, convenience, and style. With a prime location near excellent schools, bus stops, shopping centers, and the ever-popular Water World, this home is a haven for those seeking the perfect balance between comfort and accessibility. This home has been thoughtfully updated and meticulously maintained. The main level has fresh interior paint, an open kitchen layout, and sliding glass doors that lead to a backyard patio. The second level features all 4 spacious bedrooms on one level, and noteworthy improvements include a complete renovation of the main bathroom upstairs. Newly remodeled bathroom with Bluetooth speaker light and fan introduces modern fixtures and finishes. Brand-new sliding glass doors and windows on the main level come with a transferable lifetime warranty for peace of mind. The HOA has recently replaced the sewer lines, and additional amenities include a pool, clubhouse, and grounds maintenance. With thoughtful upgrades and proximity to various community amenities, this home presents an extraordinary opportunity. Don't miss out—schedule your showing today and make this delightful home your own!
